Additionally, the paper proposes a method for improving the reliability of deep learning models, which is relevant to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. The paper also mentions using saliency maps, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks, suggesting that it may also be relevant to the cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of explanations in NLP tasks, which is relevant to the cs.IR (Information Retrieval) sub-category.
